  BaseStyle->"Link"],
 " \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]negates\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] a color, giving the \
complementary color. ",
 ButtonBox["Blend",
  BaseStyle->"Link"],
 " blends a list of colors together. "
}], "Text",
 Editable->False,
 Deletable->False,
 ShowCellBracket->False],

